---
// CloseCycleButton.astro — Botón para cerrar el ciclo manualmente antes del cierre automático.
---
<button
  type="button"
  id="close-cycle-btn"
  class="close-cycle-btn"
  aria-label="Cerrar ciclo manualmente"
>
  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="close-cycle-btn-icon">
    <path d="M6 6l12 12M18 6L6 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" />
  </svg>
  <span class="close-cycle-btn-label">Cerrar ciclo ahora</span>
</button>

<dialog id="close-cycle-dialog" class="close-cycle-dialog" aria-labelledby="close-cycle-title">
  <div class="close-cycle-surface">
    <div class="close-cycle-head">
      <div>
        <p class="close-cycle-kicker">Cierre manual</p>
        <h3 id="close-cycle-title" class="close-cycle-title">¿Cerrar ciclo ahora?</h3>
      </div>
      <button type="button" id="close-cycle-close" class="close-cycle-close" aria-label="Cerrar modal">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M6 6l12 12M18 6L6 18" />
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="close-cycle-body">
      <p class="close-cycle-intro">
        Esto cerrará todos los ciclos abiertos del día en curso.
        Las operaciones que se generen después pasarán al ciclo del día siguiente.
        Úsalo solo cuando termines antes del cierre automático del sistema.
      </p>

      <div class="close-cycle-stats" id="close-cycle-stats">
        <div class="close-cycle-stat">
          <span>Veredictos abiertos</span>
          <strong id="close-cycle-open-count">--</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="close-cycle-stat">
          <span>Bs. pendientes</span>
          <strong id="close-cycle-pending-fiat">--</strong>
        </div>
      </div>

      <label class="close-cycle-label">
        <span>Motivo (opcional)</span>
        <input
          id="close-cycle-reason"
          type="text"
          maxlength="240"
          placeholder="Ej. Cierre por turno vespertino"
        />
      </label>

      <div class="close-cycle-actions">
        <button type="button" id="close-cycle-confirm">Sí, cerrar ciclo</button>
        <button type="button" id="close-cycle-cancel" class="close-cycle-secondary">Cancelar</button>
      </div>

      <p id="close-cycle-error" class="close-cycle-error" role="alert"></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</dialog>

<style is:global>
  .close-cycle-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.45);
    border-radius: 0.85rem;
    background: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.08);
    color: #fda4af;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: transform 160ms ease, background 160ms ease, border-color 160ms ease, opacity 160ms ease;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .close-cycle-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.18);
    border-color: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.7);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .close-cycle-btn:active {
    transform: scale(0.98);
  }

  .close-cycle-btn[disabled] {
    opacity: 0.55;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    transform: none;
  }

  .close-cycle-btn-icon {
    width: 0.95rem;
    height: 0.95rem;
  }

  .close-cycle-btn-label {
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .close-cycle-dialog {
    width: min(520px, calc(100vw - 2rem));
    max-width: 520px;
    padding: 0;
    border: 0;
    background: transparent;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .close-cycle-dialog::backdrop {
    background: rgba(2, 6, 12, 0.76);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .close-cycle-dialog[open] {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
  }

  .close-cycle-surface {
    width: 100%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 1.6rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(12, 16, 22, 0.98), rgba(8, 11, 16, 0.98));
    box-shadow: 0 34px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.48);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .close-cycle-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .close-cycle-kicker {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.42);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .close-cycle-title {
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .close-cycle-close {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 2.4rem;
    height: 2.4rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    transition: transform 160ms ease, background 160ms ease;
  }

  .close-cycle-close:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .close-cycle-close svg {
    width: 1rem;
    height: 1rem;
    fill: none;
    stroke: currentColor;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
    stroke-width: 2.2;
  }

  .close-cycle-body {
    padding: 1.25rem;
  }

  .close-cycle-intro {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.64);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .close-cycle-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .close-cycle-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    border-radius: 0.8rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem;
  }

  .close-cycle-stat span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .close-cycle-stat strong {
    color: #fdba74;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 950;
  }

  .close-cycle-label {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .close-cycle-label > span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .close-cycle-label input {
    width: 100%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 0.8rem;
    background: #05070a;
    color: white;
    outline: none;
    padding: 0.78rem 0.85rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: border-color 160ms ease, background 160ms ease;
  }

  .close-cycle-label input:focus {
    border-color: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.7);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  }

  .close-cycle-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }

  .close-cycle-actions button,
  .close-cycle-secondary {
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.72rem 0.9rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: transform 160ms ease, opacity 160ms ease, background 160ms ease, border-color 160ms ease;
  }

  .close-cycle-secondary {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  #close-cycle-confirm {
    flex: 1;
    border-color: rgba(251, 113, 133, 0.9);
    background: #fb7185;
    color: black;
  }

  #close-cycle-confirm:hover {
    background: #f43f5e;
  }

  .close-cycle-actions button:active,
  .close-cycle-secondary:active {
    transform: scale(0.98);
  }

  .close-cycle-error {
    min-height: 1rem;
    color: #fb7185;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .close-cycle-dialog {
      width: calc(100vw - 0.5rem);
      margin: 0.25rem;
    }

    .close-cycle-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .close-cycle-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
